snippet.textDisplay:
GOD bless you Faisal and Bilal and all the coke studio team for just this qawwali.
In this "modern" era, when young generation is distant with Qawwali and all these soulful poetry and religion, you guys brings this master piece in the play so that the new generation learn that what kind of soulful background we all had.

Thank you for this, I started crying after listening to this... You guys will know the importance of this in life hereafter... 

Rest in Peace in Sabri brothers....
